<h1>Display the Album Cover</h1>
</div>
</div>
<!--closes page header-->
<div id="taskbox">

<p>You can set up CoverSutra to display a neat Album Cover on your desktop. It displays the album artwork of the currently playing song.</p>

<div id="taskbox1">
         <div class="shadow">
                    <div id="taskframe1">
                              <div class="taskcontent">
<div class="taskprimtext">
<div class="taskprimcontent">
<p class="taskprimtextlongtext">
To display the Album Cover:</p>
</div><!--closes taskprimcontent-->
<ol id="taskauxlistnumbered">
<div class="taskauxoption">
<div class="taskauxcontent">
<li>
<p class="textlistnumber">Choose CoverSutra > Preferencesâ€¦ and click Album Cover.</p>
</li>

</div>
</div>
<div class="taskauxoption">
<div class="taskauxcontent">
<li>
<p class="textlistnumber">Click <strong>Album Cover on desktop</strong>.</p>
</li>

</div>
</div>
</ol><!--closes taskauxlistnumbered-->
</div><!-- closes taskprimtext -->

                                 </div><!--closes taskcontent-->
                      </div><!--closes taskframe1-->
           </div><!--closes shadow-->
</div><!--closes taskbox1-->

<div id="taskbox2">
         <div class="shadow">
                    <div id="taskframe2">
                              <div class="taskcontent">
<div class="taskprimtext">
<div class="taskprimcontent">
<p class="taskprimtextlongtext">
To alter it's position:</p>
</div><!--closes taskprimcontent-->
<ol id="taskauxlistnumbered">
<div class="taskauxoption">
<div class="taskauxcontent">
<li>
<p class="textlistnumber">Locate the Album Cover on your desktop.</p>
</li>

</div>
</div>
<div class="taskauxoption">
<div class="taskauxcontent">
<li>
<p class="textlistnumber">Drag and Drop to the desired position.</p>
</li>
</div>
</div>
</ol><!--closes taskauxlistnumbered-->
<p>Note: You can also show the Album Cover by choosing Show Album Cover from the status item menu.</p>
</div><!-- closes taskprimtext -->

                                 </div><!--closes taskcontent-->
                      </div><!--closes taskframe2-->
